<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
Rotatated solid shapes (also called toroids) can be created with [[Image:Part_Revolve.svg|16px]] [[Part_Revolve|Part Revolve]], too if the option {{MenuCommand|Create solid}} is checked, or with [[Image:PartDesign_Revolution.svg|16px]] [[PartDesign_Revolution|PartDesign Revolution]].
